THIS WEEK SUCKED MONKEY BALLS, this may go down as one of the worst weeks of my life, well maybe. A very long term friend of mine who was like a father to me died this week, and the worst part is the only one to blame is him. He was a big health freak, never ate red meat, didn't eat certain oils, etc etc, but he thought he was f(*&$ng superman and never had any tests run like he was supposed to when he got older to see if say.... 5 f(%*(#)ing arteries were clogged in his goddamn heart. ALL HE HAD TO FRIGGEN DO WAS HAVE A TEST, they do the op. bada bing bada boom he'd still be alive, but nooooooooo thats not how it happened. So hes gone and I cant really remember a time when ive been this down but the reality is the only one to blame is him. Even if it does sound cynical thats how i feel. Aight. Hopefully illpost withing the next few days with something a lil more positive.
